docs {
  Creates a multi-step invite for a document group.
  
  Each invite step consists of <invite_email> objects that set the email message or can disable emails all together for specific user. Invite steps also are made of the <invite_action> objects that need to be completed before the step is considered complete. Once all the invite_actions are completed, the next stepâ€™s invite emails are sent out. When all steps have been completed, completion emails are sent out.
}
